Achievements.Name: 1 of a kind
Achievements.Description: Build an ATV from scratch in the garage.

Achievements.Name: Fully Loaded
Achievements.Description: Unlock and then fill all ten ATV slots in the garage.

Achievements.Name: Mechanic
Achievements.Description: Build five ATVs, each with a different engine.

Achievements.Name: Flawless Lap
Achievements.Description: Complete a lap of a Race event in World Tour without dismounting.

Achievements.Name: Flawless Event
Achievements.Description: Complete a World Tour event without dismounting.

Achievements.Name: Tricked Out
Achievements.Description: Perform every normal trick in a single World Tour event.

Achievements.Name: Specialised
Achievements.Description: Perform 8 different special tricks in a single World Tour event.

Achievements.Name: Freestyler
Achievements.Description: Extend a Freestyle event past the third lap.

Achievements.Name: Triple Flip
Achievements.Description: During an event; pull off a 1080 forward or backward rotation in a single jump.

Achievements.Name: Nice Combo!
Achievements.Description: During an event; perform a combo of at least 50,000 points.

Achievements.Name: Sick Combo!
Achievements.Description: During an event; perform a combo of at least 125,000 points.

Achievements.Name: Killer Combo!
Achievements.Description: During an event; perform a combo of at least 250,000 points.

Achievements.Name: You're special!
Achievements.Description: During an event; perform every special trick in the game.

Achievements.Name: Pure perfection
Achievements.Description: Come first in every event in the Pure World Tour

Achievements.Name: Grease Monkey
Achievements.Description: Earn a 1st place with every engine type in World Tour Mode

Achievements.Name: Comeback Kid
Achievements.Description: Come from last place on the last lap to win a race event in World Tour Mode

Achievements.Name: Fresh Air
Achievements.Description: Win a competitive Freestyle event with Fresh tricks only.

Achievements.Name: No Messing
Achievements.Description: Complete World Tour Mode while participating in a maximum of 42 events

Achievements.Name: Zero to Hero
Achievements.Description: Acquire a special trick within 30 seconds of starting a Race event.

Achievements.Name: You reckon?
Achievements.Description: Pull a special trick during a Sprint event.

Achievements.Name: Two time!
Achievements.Description: Perform two special tricks in one jump.

Achievements.Name: Hang Time
Achievements.Description: Spend 150 seconds in the air and go on to win the event.

Achievements.Name: Learner Driver
Achievements.Description: Lap another rider during an offline Sprint event.

Achievements.Name: No pain, no gain.
Achievements.Description: Crash more than ten times and still win a competitive Race or Sprint event.

Achievements.Name: Full speed ahead.
Achievements.Description: Hold down the accelerator for an entire competitive Race or Sprint event and finish in first place.

Achievements.Name: Show Off
Achievements.Description: Win a Race or Sprint event and crossing the line doing a Wheelie on every lap.

Achievements.Name: Win Online
Achievements.Description: Come first in an online event.

Achievements.Name: 5 in a row
Achievements.Description: Come first in 5 online events in a row.

Achievements.Name: Underdog
Achievements.Description: Use a class D engine to beat an opponent with a class A engine in a ranked match

Achievements.Name: Online Champ
Achievements.Description: Come first in a online championship.
